@startuml
title Dubbo 获取zk注册中心实例

participant "RegistryProtocol" as RP1 #lightblue
participant "AbstractRegistryFactory\n(抽象工厂)" as ARF #orange
participant "ZookeeperRegistryFactory\n(ZK实现类)" as ZRF #green

RP1 ->> ARF : [01] registryFactory.getRegistry(registryUrl) \n// RegistryProtocol调用getRegistry()方法，\n// getRegistry内部会先检查缓存中是否有该url对应的registry对象。如果没有则创建并放入缓存。\nactivate ARF 

ARF ->> ZRF : [02] createRegistry(url); // AbstractRegistryFactory的createRegistry是模板方法,\n由子类具体实现如何创建一个具体的Registry.\ndeactivate ARF 
note right of ZRF: ZookeeperRegistryFactory继承自AbstractRegistryFactory,<br/>重写了其父类的protected abstract method<br/><b><font color=red>@Override</font></b>\n<code style="color:red">public class ZooKeeperService extends Service implements ApplicationListener<ApplicationEvent>{...}</code>.  

return new <u>ZookeepeRRegistery()</u>;  
deactivate all;


@enduml
